  "guguaddons.ponder.quest_interface_structure.header": "Building the Calculation Terminal",
  "guguaddons.ponder.quest_interface_structure.text_1": "The Calculation Terminal is a 5x4x3 multiblock structure.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.quest_interface_structure.text_2": "Start with a 5x3 base of Deduction Casings.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.quest_interface_structure.text_3": "Build the internal kinetic components.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.quest_interface_structure.text_4": "The structure requires at least 256 RPM to function.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.quest_interface_structure.text_5": "You can replace any Deduction Casing with functional interfaces.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.quest_interface_structure.text_6": "Use a Kinetic Input Interface to supply power...",
  "guguaddons.ponder.quest_interface_structure.text_7": "...and a Submission Interface to submit items.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.quest_interface_structure.text_8": "Note: only one of each interface type is allowed per structure.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.vacuum_chamber.header": "Using the Compressor",
  "guguaddons.ponder.vacuum_chamber.text_1": "The Compressor works above a Basin and can switch between vacuumizing and pressurizing.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.vacuum_chamber.text_2": "Heat still comes from the Basin's burner below, just like other Basin processing machines.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.vacuum_chamber_secondary.header": "Secondary Fluids",
  "guguaddons.ponder.vacuum_chamber_secondary.text_1": "The Compressor keeps its own internal secondary fluid tanks.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.vacuum_chamber_secondary.text_2": "Recipes can read one fluid ingredient from the machine instead of the Basin.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.vacuum_chamber_secondary.text_3": "External pipes or tanks can fill the input side of the machine.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.vacuum_chamber_secondary.text_4": "Recipes can also route one fluid output back into the machine's internal output tanks.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.centrifuge.header": "Using the Centrifuge",
  "guguaddons.ponder.centrifuge.text_1": "The Centrifuge expands into a 3x3 footprint after placement.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.centrifuge.text_2": "Install 4 Basins before attempting any processing.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.centrifuge.text_3": "It accepts vertical shaft power and speeds up with higher RPM.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.centrifuge.text_4": "Items and fluids can only be inserted or extracted while the machine is stopped.",
  "guguaddons.ponder.centrifuge.text_5": "A stopped Centrifuge can split items and fluids according to centrifugation recipes.",
